                        <h4 class="panel-title">
                            <a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#example-accordion" href="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">California Civil Liberties Public Education Program (CCLPEP)</a>
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseThree" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingThree">
                        <div class="panel-body">
                            The purpose of the <a href="/grants/civil-liberties/">California Civil Liberties Public Education program</a> is to sponsor public educational activities and development of educational materials to ensure that the events surrounding the exclusion, forced removal, and internment of civilians and permanent resident aliens of Japanese ancestry will be remembered so that the causes and circumstance of this and similar events may be illuminated and understood. This program is administered by the California State Library.
                        </div>
                    </div>
